link: https://MahmoudEzzat8824.github.io/Digilians-Remainder/

Email reminders are sent by GitHub Actions from `.github/workflows/email-reminders.yml`.

Required GitHub Secrets:
- `SENDGRID_API_KEY`
- `SENDGRID_FROM_EMAIL`
- `CONTACTS_SHEET_URL` for the Google Sheet that contains instructor names/numbers and emails
- `INSTRUCTOR_EMAILS_JSON` as JSON, for example: `{"Instructor Name":"name@example.com"}`

The schedule is set to `0 20 * * *` which means 8:00 PM UTC. If you want 8:00 PM in your local timezone, convert it to UTC and update the cron value.

The contacts sheet must be publicly readable or published to the web so GitHub Actions can fetch it.